code: @Override public void execute() {     UpdateItemResult result = ddbClient.updateItem(new UpdateItemRequest().withTableName(determineTableName()).withKey(determineKey()).withAttributeUpdates(determineUpdateValues()).withExpected(determineUpdateCondition()).withReturnValues(determineReturnValues())).     addAttributesToResult(result.getAttributes()). }
